Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Here's something\Nfor your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NThank you, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty good ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the\NMeat Ball of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You cooks should\Nnot have defied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give you\Nslime balls an order...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You will follow it\Ndown to the last letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever disobey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about a hundred meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take it to your\Nmen right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NNo, Owner Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Red Foot Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Protect Baratie! The\NGreat Pirate, Red Foot Zeff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What're you doing?!\NYou can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK T] If all of those\Npirates get their strength back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the restaurant will be\Ncompletely taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NThat would be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...if they still had\Nthe will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NTell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your will survive defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That... can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Don Krieg\Nwas defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Not even he could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate fleet with\N50 ships couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,make it on the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NIt is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Red Foot Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NSo, you are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The unrivaled pirate captain\Nwho was also the ship's cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right,\NI'm still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But what has any of this\Ngot to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been a pirate\Nfor many years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose the life of a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chose the life of a cook," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have\Na choice, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You live as a cook because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing you\Ncan be now is a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was known far and wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Foot Zeff was a\Nmaster of deadly kicks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who never used his\Nhands in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said that\Nwith his mighty legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he could crush bedrock to sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave footprints\Non solid steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Red Foot" referred to his\Nboots which became soaked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the blood of his enemies\Nas he kicked them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it really is a pity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that you no longer have\Nthat precious leg of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that rumor\Nsome time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How unlucky for you to have\Nsuch an accident at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that your greatest weapon\Nhas been sacrificed to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you're defenseless,\Ncompletely unable to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NI don't need to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as I have\Nmy two hands for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough chitchat,\Nlet's get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Red... Foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the man who\Nsailed the perilous waters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Grand Line and\Ncame back unscathed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a logbook\Ndetailing your tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a full year of your\Njourney there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! So is he sayin'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been to the\NGrand Line too, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My logbook, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I do indeed\Nhave a record of my travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will never\Nhand it over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignorant brute...\NThat logbook is sacred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the pride of the\Ncrewmen that I sailed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far too important\Nto give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It's true that\Nthe Grand Line beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... I will\Nnever give up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it's\Njust another ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I had enough weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...and men...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] Regrettably, the only\Nthing I lacked was information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'll fix all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I have your logbook,\NI'll form another pirate fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and seize the\Nlegendary One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will stand as ruler\Nof this great pirate era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNow, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me who's gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS gasp]\N--[COOK U] Chore Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't be such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You better back off, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, not from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow that kind\Nof stupidity again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, well, stupid or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just stating the\Nfacts like they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still gonna conquer\Nthe Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]\NNo, you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that we didn't have\Nthe information we needed;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but my fleet of five\Nthousand men was wiped out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in just seven days, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That sea is hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! One week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg's ships were\Nwiped out in seven days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK KK]\NWhat happened out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't find your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,smart-assed remarks\Nvery amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on\Nthis foolish behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you right\Nhere and right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI can, and I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be my pleasure to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,send you to an early\Ngrave, you cocky runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Luffy?\NYou need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't need help,\Nthat's okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, guys.\NAppreciate the offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can\Nhandle this clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you say you don't need\Nany help, who am I to argue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Us awesome fighters are\Njust gonna sit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Holler if you need us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWhat'd you do that for Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NShut up already, you weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those two guys your "crew"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty small\Ngroup you got there, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got two more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a part of your crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI'll deal with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm going\Nto go feed my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who\Ndon't wish to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can leave the restaurant\Nnow and escape that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only things I'm after are\Nthe logbook and this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] However, if you wish\Nto stay and be slaughtered...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no problem burying every\Nlast one of you at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It just got really quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Big Bro Zoro is in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, everything should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NYeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if it's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NGood point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go in there, too?\NWhaddya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[smooch]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY gag]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine!\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU, JOHNNY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groaning]\NI'm... so sorry, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it\Nwould be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] You have nothing\Nto apologize for, sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NEvery cook at this restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,did what they thought was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is\Nto say about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting as if\Nyou're taking Sanji's side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This mess is his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK V]\NHe's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji is responsible for\Nthis whole damn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Boss! That man's gonna\Nput your precious restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,None of you have any\Nidea what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be on the brink\Nof starvation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To have no food or water\Non the open ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way you could\Npossibly understand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what a terrifying\Nprospect that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most difficult\Nsituation a man can ever face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're\Ntalkin' about, Chef Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] The difference\Nbetween all of you and Sanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that Sanji knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NWhat's the boss trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C] Yeah, what's he\Nsaying that Sanji knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] If all you're gonna\Ndo is stand around grumbling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--then leave this place\N--[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] I, for one,\Nam gonna stay and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't live with myself\Nif I accepted defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK W]\NI'm staying, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is our\Nrestaurant, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, and this place\Nis all I've got, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw how powerful\NDon is, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHey, Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up because I'm only\Ngoing to say this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeding someone who's hungry\Nis my sacred moral duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that your crew is well fed,\NI have no obligation to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With a clean conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can beat every last one\Nof them to a bloody pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone tries to\Ntake the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them without a\Nmoment's hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] Hah! You're a\Nreal head-case, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting him live, then\Nthreatening to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it, cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSee? This guy's awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares how awesome he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out\Nof here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy there, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Don Krieg, but he's\Nin pretty sad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm. Hey, Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you didn't know\Nanything about the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought you'd been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing makes any sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to us\Non the seventh day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of our journey through\Nthat cursed sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if\Nit was a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...or reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw things that I can't\Nbring myself to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know in my heart that\Nit's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...for that entire\N50 ship fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be completely\Neradicated by a single man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp, whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NIt all happened so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as this man appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,he began to systematically sink\Nour ships one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] If that raging storm\Nhadn't come upon us when it did,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then that monster would have\Ndestroyed our flagship as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] I don't know if a\Nsingle other ship made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It all seems like a terrible\Nnightmare burned into my memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They were like a hawk's,\Nsharp and murderous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His gaze alone felt like\Nthe cold hand of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat did he just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NWell then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That can only be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--known as Hawk-Eye.\N--[COOK B] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Your description\Nof his heartless gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't proof of his identity\Nin and of itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the way he so easily\Ndecimated your fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,confirms without a\Ndoubt, that it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know him, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man I've\Nbeen looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye is the whole\Nreason I set out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Could that man\Nhave had some kind of score
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to settle with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NWe didn't do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Perhaps you\Ndisturbed him during a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he destroy an entire\Nfleet for something so trivial?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF chuckles]\NThere's no reason to shout...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might like\Na little friendly advice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on what kind of a place\Nthe Grand Line is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And what kind of place is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably means that\Nanything can happen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! Do we really,\Nreally have to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, USOPP]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey... Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NThat's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be such a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand\Nthe concept of "danger"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NFinally, my life's goal will
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,be achieved on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out there somewhere,\Nand I'm gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NAre you that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's idiots like you\Nguys that end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NThat may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But lay off the name-calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I devoted my entire life to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming the world's\Ngreatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm the only one who\Ngets to call me stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, right?! I mean,\Nit only seems fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI sighs]\NWhat morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do any of you maggots understand\Nthe current situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That enormous galleon moored\Nin front of our dear little
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,restaurant is none other\Nthan Don Krieg's flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't we check back into\Nreality and deal with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]\NYeah! We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NI can't believe it! We're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NIt's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NNightmare's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D] We sailed into\Nthe pirate graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but we came back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... And I'm\Nglad you all made it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'll need a healthy crew\Nto go back to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Why the long faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... Why are we\Ngoing back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Point taken... Are there\Nany other objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] First, we need to take\Nover that floating restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we can abandon the wreck\Nwe're on before it falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the enemy;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they're just a bunch\Nof prissy cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't take much\Nto crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Attack!\N--[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?! They're\Ngonna be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C]\NThe restaurant is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll fight to the\Ndeath to keep it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE LL]\NDon Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The main ship... It was cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was cut?! What\Ndo you mean "cut"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something sliced\Nup this galleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp, scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we'll sink along with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK H]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Nami and the guys are\Nstill on our ship out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groans]\NI hope it's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY pants, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NBig Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYosaku! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAre you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat happened to the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Nami? Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NI'm sorry, Big Bro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to say\Nthis, but... she's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] See ya! Oh, and\Nmake sure to tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] If it's meant to be,\NI'll see them real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She took all the treasure\Nand sailed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NShe did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He followed us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[heartbeat thumps]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him... He's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That's the man\NI've been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd\Nsee him this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.91,0:24:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou gonna fight him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Yeah, that's the whole\Nreason I set out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.54,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey, Zoro, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] So this is the\Nworld's greatest swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really this\Nmuch weaker than him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP]\NZoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hawk-Eye Mihawk! The Great\NSwordsman Zoro Falls At Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

